div.div:
“LycoReco” is a café with a traditional Japanese twist located in downtown Tokyo. But the delicious coffee and sugary sweets are not the only orders this café takes! From delivering packages short distances, to pick-ups and drop-offs on the lonely streets at night, to zombies and giant monster extermination…?! Whatever your problem, we're here to help! We will solve any kind of "trouble" you may have!
Waiting for you are the ever-smiling poster-girl and the cool, serious newcomer. A petite girl who never wants to work and a young woman approaching thirty who wants to get married. And the manager is a nice guy who’s obsessed with Japan!
Whatever your order is, leave it all up to us♪
(Source: Official Site)
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

The second season of Hataraku Maou-sama! MgRonald’s best demon lord worker is back, climbing the corporate ladder to become ruler of Earth. But Maou’s plans of domination might need to be put on hold when a small girl claims to be his and Emi’s child! (Source: Crunchyroll)
Jimi de Medatanai Watashi wa, Kyou de Owari ni Shimasu.

Elaine Lana Norris, who was born at the top of the aristocratic ladder, was suddenly abandoned by her fiancé for another and had her engagement to him broken off. Made out to be a villainess by her ex-fiancé's lover and her entourage, she is subsequently driven out of her home by the strict grandfather who raised her. With this exiled life however, Lana's true skills and desires can finally bloom as the owner of an inn!
Tsuihou Sareta Onimotsu Tamer, Sekai Yuiitsu no Necromancer ni Kakusei Suru: The Tale of the Necromancer.

Recon, mapping, carrying baggage, cooking, keeping watch, taking blows… even while doing all these things, the tamer, Randall, is called a burden and useless by his party members.
This S-ranked party is filled with genius magicians, excellent swordsmen, famous priests, and great knights, that show superb teamwork and drive, which helped them become the most famous party in the country.
But despite being incredibly popular, the members of the party feel dissatisfied with Randall. He soon gets kicked out just while he was gaining influence of his own and unlocks his true power while seeking for his revenge.

div.span: Turbulent Adventurers are Introverted, Observant, Feeling, Prospecting and Turbulent. They tend to have open minds, approaching life, new experiences, and people with grounded warmth.
Likely prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Likely pragmatic and down-to-earth, with a strong focus on what is happening or very likely to happen.
Likely values emotional expression and sensitivity, prioritizing empathy, social harmony, and cooperation.
Likely very good at improvising and adapting. Tends to be flexible and values novelty above stability.
Likely self-conscious, sensitive to stress, success-driven, perfectionistic, and eager to improve.
